data.value: SELECT DISTINCT ' ' LAB_NO , B.SPECIMEN_SER , MIN(B.BUNHO) , MIN(FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME2(B.BUNHO)) SUNAME2 , MIN(FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA,SYSDATE)) , MIN(B.HO_DONG) , B.PART_JUBSU_DATE , B.PART_JUBSU_TIME , MIN(B.PART_JUBSUJA) , MIN(B.JUBSUJA) --, B.JUNDAL_GUBUN , MAX(DECODE(B.IN_OUT_GUBUN, 'O', C.ORDER_REMARK, A.ORDER_REMARK )) REMARK , MIN(DECODE(B.PART_JUBSU_DATE,NULL,'N','Y')) PART_JUBSU_FLAG , 0 FKOCS , MIN(B.IN_OUT_GUBUN) , MIN(B.DOCTOR_NAME) , MIN(E.CODE_NAME) TUBE_NAME , MIN(B.EMERGENCY) EMERGENCY --, MAX(DECODE(B.SUNAB_DATE,NULL,'N','Y')) SUNAB_YN , MAX(DECODE(B.IN_OUT_GUBUN, 'O', C.IF_DATA_SEND_YN , A.IF_DATA_SEND_YN )) SUNAB_YN , MAX(DECODE(B.RESULT_DATE,NULL,'N','Y')) RESULT_YN , MAX(DECODE(F.CODE,NULL,'N','Y')) LABEL_ONE_MORE FROM CPL0109 F, CPL0109 E, CPL0109 D, OCS1003 C, CPL2010 B, OCS2003 A WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND D.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND E.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND F.HOSP_CODE(+) = B.HOSP_CODE AND B.PART_JUBSU_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_part_jubsu_date,'YYYY/MM/DD') --AND B.JUNDAL_GUBUN LIKE '%' AND NVL(B.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' AND D.CODE_TYPE = '01' AND D.CODE = B.JUNDAL_GUBUN AND E.CODE_TYPE(+) = '02' AND E.CODE (+) = B.TUBE_CODE AND B.FKOCS1003 = C.PKOCS1003 (+) AND B.FKOCS2003 = A.PKOCS2003 (+) AND F.CODE_TYPE(+) = '21' -- 튜브 한장더 뇨관련 AND F.CODE(+) = B.TUBE_CODE AND B.SPECIMEN_SER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY B.PART_JUBSU_DATE,B.PART_JUBSU_TIME,B.SPECIMEN_SER,B.JUNDAL_GUBUN ORDER BY B.SPECIMEN_SER DESC--, B.JUNDAL_GUBUN DESC
